OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCrackdown on pavement      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fparking begins in Edinburgh
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Motorists in Edinburgh now face a #100 
OL,6, fine for parking on pavements, as the  
OL,7, city council becomes the first in      
OL,8, Scotland to implement the ban.         
OL,10,FThe rules are designed to protect      
OL,11,Fpedestrians, especially people in      
OL,12,Fwheelchairs and those pushing buggies. 
OL,14,FBut BBC Scotland News has also spoken  
OL,15,Fto people worried it could lead to     
OL,16,Fproblems for bin lorries and emergency 
OL,17,Fservice vehicles on narrow streets.    
OL,19,FThe council said pavement parking was a
OL,20,F"persistent issue" on 500 streets.     
